data.description: Fantastic first time homebuyer opportunity!!! This cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bath home features a mother in law floor plan. The kitchen and dining area are open to the living room for maximum use of space. The sit at bar is perfect for guests. Kitchen features tile flooring, large sink and pantry.  Owner has upgraded to laminate flooring giving the home a fresh new look.(most areas) Large master bedroom with faux blinds, ceiling fan and carpet. Masterbath has a waking closet and walk-in shower. 33ft X12 ft extended covered patio recently added. Excellent for entertaining and still plenty of yard space for kids and pets.
